### 4. **Entity/Models Layer** (Domain Models)
**Location:** `Models/`

**หน้าที่:**
- กำหนด Data Structure
- Data Transfer Objects (DTOs)
- Domain Entities
- Request/Response Models

**ประเภทของ Models:**

#### 4.1 **Entity Models** (Domain Models)
```csharp
// Models/Entities/Appoint.cs
public class Appoint
{
    public string Id { get; set; }
    public string CustomerId { get; set; }
    public DateTime AppointDate { get; set; }
    public string BranchCode { get; set; }
    public string Status { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreatedDate { get; set; }
    public string CreatedBy { get; set; }
}
```

#### 4.2 **Request Models** (DTOs)
```csharp
// Models/Requests/AppointRequest.cs
public class AppointRequest
{
    [Required]
    public string CustomerId { get; set; }
    
    [Required]
    public DateTime AppointDate { get; set; }
    
    [Required]
    public string BranchCode { get; set; }
}
```

#### 4.3 **Response Models** (DTOs)
```csharp
// Models/Responses/AppointResponse.cs
public class AppointResponse
{
    public string Id { get; set; }
    public string CustomerId { get; set; }
    public DateTime AppointDate { get; set; }
    public string BranchCode { get; set; }
    public string Status { get; set; }
}
```

**Naming Convention:**
- Entity: `{EntityName}.cs`
- Request: `{EntityName}Request.cs` หรือ `Create{EntityName}Request.cs`
- Response: `{EntityName}Response.cs`

