### 5. **Data Access Layer** (Repository Pattern)
**Location:** `DataAccess/`

**หน้าที่:**
- เข้าถึง Database
- CRUD Operations
- Query ข้อมูล
- Transaction Management

**โครงสร้าง:**
```
DataAccess/
├── DBContext/
│   └── ApplicationDbContext.cs
├── Repositories/
│   ├── AppointRepository.cs
│   └── CustomerRepository.cs
└── Interfaces/
    ├── IAppointRepository.cs
    └── ICustomerRepository.cs
```

**ตัวอย่าง Repository:**
```csharp
public class AppointRepository : IAppointRepository
{
    private readonly ApplicationDbContext _context;
    
    public AppointRepository(ApplicationDbContext context)
    {
        _context = context;
    }
    
    public async Task<Appoint> InsertAsync(Appoint appoint)
    {
        await _context.Appoints.AddAsync(appoint);
        await _context.SaveChangesAsync();
        return appoint;
    }
    
    public async Task<Appoint> GetByIdAsync(string id)
    {
        return await _context.Appoints
            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(x => x.Id == id);
    }
    
    public async Task<bool> UpdateAsync(Appoint appoint)
    {
        _context.Appoints.Update(appoint);
        return await _context.SaveChangesAsync() > 0;
    }
}
```

**กฎการใช้งาน:**
- ✅ ใช้ Entity Framework Core หรือ Dapper
- ✅ Implement Interface
- ✅ Handle Database Exceptions
- ❌ ห้ามมี Business Logic
- ✅ ควรใช้ Async/Await

**Naming Convention:**
- ชื่อไฟล์: `{EntityName}Repository.cs`
- ชื่อ Class: `{EntityName}Repository`

---

### 6. **Database Context Layer**
**Location:** `DataAccess/DBContext/`

**หน้าที่:**
- กำหนด DbContext สำหรับ Entity Framework
- Configuration ของ Database Connection
- Entity Configurations

**ตัวอย่าง:**
```csharp
public class ApplicationDbContext : DbContext
{
    public ApplicationDbContext(DbContextOptions<ApplicationDbContext> options)
        : base(options)
    {
    }
    
    public DbSet<Appoint> Appoints { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Customer> Customers { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Branch> Branches { get; set; }
    
    protected override void OnModelCreating(ModelBuilder modelBuilder)
    {
        base.OnModelCreating(modelBuilder);
        
        // Entity Configurations
        modelBuilder.Entity<Appoint>(entity =>
        {
            entity.HasKey(e => e.Id);
            entity.Property(e => e.Id).HasMaxLength(50);
            entity.Property(e => e.Status).HasMaxLength(20);
        });
    }
}
```

