## Sequence Diagram - Request Flow

### Create Appointment Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant Controller as AppointController
    participant Service as AppointService
    participant Repo as AppointRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>+Controller: POST /api/appoint
    Note over Controller: Validate ModelState

    Controller->>+Service: CreateAppointAsync(request)
    Note over Service: Business Validation
    Note over Service: Transform Request → Entity

    Service->>+Repo: InsertAsync(appoint)
    Repo->>+DB: INSERT INTO Appoints
    DB-->>-Repo: Success
    Repo-->>-Service: Appoint Entity

    Note over Service: Transform Entity → Response
    Service-->>-Controller: AppointResponse

    Controller-->>-Client: 200 OK + JSON Response
```

### Get Appointment with Error Handling

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant MW as Middleware
    participant Controller as AppointController
    participant Service as AppointService
    participant Cache as MemcachedService
    participant Repo as AppointRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>+MW: GET /api/appoint/{id}
    MW->>+Controller: Authenticated Request

    Controller->>+Service: GetAppointByIdAsync(id)

    Service->>+Cache: GetAsync(key)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Service: Cached Data
    else Cache Miss
        Cache-->>-Service: null
        Service->>+Repo: GetByIdAsync(id)
        Repo->>+DB: SELECT * FROM Appoints
        DB-->>-Repo: Row Data
        Repo-->>-Service: Appoint Entity
    end

    alt Found
        Service-->>Controller: AppointResponse
        Controller-->>Client: 200 OK
    else Not Found
        Service-->>-Controller: throw BusinessException
        Controller-->>-MW: Exception
        MW-->>-Client: 404 Not Found
    end
```

